                  watchdog_enable PROC
;;;14077  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;14078  void watchdog_enable (void)

;;;14079  {
;;;14080  LPC_WDT->WDTC=2000000;

;;;14082  LPC_WDT->WDMOD=3;

0142dc  7001              STRB     r1,[r0,#0]
;;;14083  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;
0142de  f04f01aa          MOV      r1,#0xaa
0142e2  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;14084  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;
0142e4  f04f0155          MOV      r1,#0x55
0142e8  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;14085  }
0142ea  4770              BX       lr

                          ENDP

                  watchdog_reset PROC
;;;14087  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;14088  void watchdog_reset (void)

;;;14089  {
;;;14090  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;

;;;14091  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;

0142fa  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;14092  }
0142fc  4770              BX       lr
;;;14093  
                          ENDP

                  SysTick_Handler PROC
;;;14099  //***********************************************
;;;14100  void SysTick_Handler (void) 	 /* SysTick Interrupt Handler (1ms)    */

;;;14102  //sys_plazma++;
